WEBVTT

00:04:05.811 --> 00:04:08.077
I didn't like what I saw.

00:04:08.077 --> 00:04:09.496
It took me a while,

00:04:09.496 --> 00:04:12.738
but eventually I refused
to serve in the West Bank

00:04:12.738 --> 00:04:15.594
and had to spend time in jail.

00:04:15.594 --> 00:04:16.754
It was a bit —

00:04:16.754 --> 00:04:19.730
(Applause) —

00:04:19.730 --> 00:04:21.422
It was not that bad, I have to say.

00:04:21.422 --> 00:04:24.505
It was a bit like being in a hotel,
but with very shitty food.

00:04:24.505 --> 00:04:26.170
(Laughter)

00:04:26.170 --> 00:04:30.042
In jail, I kept thinking 
that I need people to know.